sequenceDiagram
    actor Student
    participant StudentDashboard as Student Dashboard
    participant DashboardController as Dashboard Controller
    participant KnowledgeModel as Knowledge Model (FSRS)
    participant Database

    Note over Student, Database: UC-08: View Topics (Dashboard & Progress)

    Student->>StudentDashboard: Lands on Home/Dashboard
    StudentDashboard->>DashboardController: getStudentProgress(studentId)
    DashboardController->>Database: fetchTopicMastery(studentId)
    Database-->>DashboardController: return mastery_records (stability, difficulty, next_review)
    
    Note right of DashboardController: Step 4: Prioritize using FSRS retrievability
    DashboardController->>KnowledgeModel: calculateRetrievability(mastery_data)
    KnowledgeModel-->>DashboardController: list of priority_scores
    DashboardController->>DashboardController: Categorize (Due vs. Future) & Sort by Score
    DashboardController-->>StudentDashboard: return dashboard_payload (topics, tiers, status)

    alt Nothing Due (Flow 3a)
        StudentDashboard-->>Student: Display "All caught up! 🎉" & "Study Ahead" suggestions
    else Topics Due
        StudentDashboard-->>Student: Render topics with Tier badges (🥉, , 🥇) & "Review!" tags
    end

    opt Search/Filter (Flow 5a)
        Student->>StudentDashboard: Enters search query (e.g., "Modus Ponens")
        StudentDashboard->>DashboardController: searchTopics(query)
        DashboardController->>Database: findTopics(query)
        Database-->>DashboardController: match_results
        DashboardController-->>StudentDashboard: display filtered topics
        StudentDashboard-->>Student: Updated list view
    end

    Student->>StudentDashboard: Selects a topic to practice
    StudentDashboard-->>Student: Trigger UC-03: Solve Practice Sheet (Adaptive)